text: Miroslav Forte (born 24 October 1911, date of death unknown) was a Slovenian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1911 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Slovenian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:People from Trbovlje
